{"tid":969573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成績突飛猛進也不行？非裔生考太好被疑作弊","createTime":"2019-01-05T07:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T16:19:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6d304aefe6305e1e0cefff5e44d14f085e6052ec","tid":969573,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"佛羅里達州一名非裔女高中生，因為學術水準測驗考試（SAT）成績突飛猛進，被當局取消資格，錯失如期進入目標學校的機會。女高中生堅稱從未作弊，並請來知名民權律師，討回公道。<br />\n現年18歲女高中生坎貝爾（Kamilah Campbell），去年三月考SAT，只得900分。為了心儀的佛羅里達州立大學，她的母親請了家教，讓女兒報讀補習班，也讓她買參考書狂練，去年10月考獲1,230分，比前一次考試足足多了330分。<br />\n不過，坎貝爾其後收到美國教育測驗服務社（Educational Testing Services，簡稱ETS）來信，指她的考試分數異常（anomalies），裁定成績無效。由於覆核分數需時四至六星期，坎貝爾錯過今年1月1日向大學呈交分數的期限，無法如期升學。<br />\n坎貝爾感到非常氣憤，請來知名律師克倫普（Benjamin Crump），為自己討回公道。她召開記者會強調沒有作弊，讀書是為了實現夢想，「不會讓ETS褫奪我的夢想。」<br />\n克倫普是佛羅里達州立大學校友，對坎貝爾的遭遇感到氣憤，質疑ETS對非裔學生有偏見，認為非裔不可能單靠努力而學業進步。克倫普指出，ETS做法阻礙了當事人申請奬學金，構成當事人的財務負擔。<br />\n坎貝爾的高中老師艾斯特拉達（Julio Estrada）也出面表示，她是個好學生，GPA有3.1分，從未見過她有不誠實行為，深信她全靠勤奮換取好成績。邁阿密戴德郡教育局對事件表示關注，認為ETS的指控令人困擾，當局不得不介入。<br />\n負責舉辦SAT考試的美國大學理事會（The College Board）表示，不會單靠成績高低，來判斷考生是否有可疑，強調ETS沒有在信中稱坎貝爾因分數增加才被審查。（北美中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6SPsOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6SPsOk.png&h=467cf390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a66b25e59eb207683dad1dcf7fb808596c5085e3","tid":969573,"uid":156363,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"合理懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb01d00493f1484ce5b74388d77422ac65f2b9a","tid":969573,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":69,"score":-68,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"有料既怕咩下年再考？"},{"pid":"d58230953dd565c9d337e64296022ba298a3f850","tid":969573,"uid":38651,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"衝上雲霄吳卓羲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f73e3140efb5bc9dd86332406db1c88edac34c","tid":969573,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"左膠：迫害少數族裔同迫害女性"},{"pid":"cf38b6908fe14f4ab26fb86202ef910dd583c8af","tid":969573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"好可疑"},{"pid":"1aaefc89a076df5cd982cf1a763841ff1851f1e3","tid":969573,"uid":52068,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"如果未查就取消資格嘅都幾癲下"},{"pid":"1c7027012fd8e149cd83b5dfd5d39462296d1ec7","tid":969573,"uid":24519,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"5bb01d00493f1484ce5b74388d77422ac65f2b9a","tid":969573,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":69,"score":-68,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"有料既怕咩下年再考？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"你真係on撚9到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c369d8d896023bd50de4510c1f6ee2825201000","tid":969573,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"Night School<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b571cfb0eb4112607b22a56d6a25302f9f651bff","tid":969573,"uid":60287,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"&quot;&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">指她的考試分數異常（anomalies）</span>&quot;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;&quot;強調ETS沒有在信中稱坎貝爾<span style=\"color: red;\">因分數增加</span>才被審查&quot;&quot;<br />\n<br />\n語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b90f30f6a4b1afa48b382ff06a0b949223d705","tid":969573,"uid":2471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"i am going to say the n word"},{"pid":"aa3731738be6f0632f35150d4bec3c7e195d6d5e","tid":969573,"uid":193642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5bb01d00493f1484ce5b74388d77422ac65f2