"msg":"即係其實分數差成三分一，都應該懷疑下嘅<br />\n但應該判咗有問題先取消資格囉<br />\n搞到人地入唔到U，又真係衰咗啲"},{"pid":"5e1a1d8ea1329ff8002c285399e1538a879d5114","tid":969573,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"053665b1990f8c2601d60e43cf9d3e32637a59b6","tid":969573,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"cdc267b9d9b27131f2615c873442485c262bdfb6","tid":969573,"uid":105678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"如果真係畀人屈，係應該幫佢討回公道嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"即係其實分數差成三分一，都應該懷疑下嘅<br />\n但應該判咗有問題先取消資格囉<br />\n搞到人地入唔到U，又真係衰咗啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"只係三分之一進步就 DQ<br />\n<br />\n追三個 grade姐<br />\n<br />\nbtw今次啲回覆好開明"},{"pid":"b530618a260e233ea8c6f0fc291a4d766c82ab0e","tid":969573,"uid":53374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cnn.com/2019/01/02/us/florida-girl-sat-controversy/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnn.com%2F2019%2F01%2F02%2Fus%2Fflorida-girl-sat-controversy%2Findex.html&d=WjS%2FZSaLopgR6AnXVgGLELIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8d569396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcnn.com%2F2019%2F01%2F02%2Fus%2Fflorida-girl-sat-controversy%2Findex.html&h=9b367aa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://cnn.com/2019/01/02/us/florida-girl-sat-controversy/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n話佢出貓嘅原因係佢啲答案同其他考生好似"},{"pid":"8fa0fae25dca6dc27f212f229654b3235d018229","tid":969573,"uid":208159,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:14:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71de562227b4045eec03143fd5d202021053b3d6","tid":969573,"uid":60287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b530618a260e233ea8c6f0fc291a4d766c82ab0e","tid":969573,"uid":53374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cnn.com/2019/01/02/us/florida-girl-sat-controversy/index.html\" data-sr-url=